[Verse 1: Meghan Trainor]
I found myself dreamin' in silver and gold
Like a scene from a movie that every broken heart knows
We were walkin' on moonlight and you pulled me close
Split second and you disappeared and then I was all alone

[Pre-Chorus: Meghan Trainor]
I woke up in tears, with you by my side
A breath of relief, and I've realised
No, we're not promised tomorrow

[Chorus: Meghan Trainor]
So I'm gonna love you like I'm gonna lose you
I'm gonna hold you like I'm saying goodbye
Wherever we're standin', I won't take you for granted
'Cause we'll never know when, when we'll run out of time
So I'm gonna love you like I'm gonna lose you (Lose you)
I'm gonna love you like I'm gonna lose you

[Verse 2: John Legend, Meghan Trainor]
In the blink of an eye, just a whisper of smoke
You could lose everything, the truth is you never know
So I'll kiss you longer, babe (Hey), any chance that I get
I'll make the most of the minutes and love with no regret

[Pre-Chorus: John Legend, Meghan Trainor, Both]

'Cause no (No), we're not promised tomorrow


[Chorus: Meghan Trainor, John Legend, Both]

I'm gonna hold you (Hey), like I'm saying goodbye
Wherever we're standin' (Yeah), I won't take you for granted
'Cause we'll never know when, when we'll run out of time
So I'm gonna love you (I'm gonna love you), like I'm gonna lose you (Like I'm gonna lose you)
I'm gonna love you (Love you), like I'm gonna lose you (Hey)

[Instrumental Bridge]

[Chorus: Meghan Trainor, John Legend, Both]
I'm gonna love you (Oh) like I'm gonna lose you (Like I'm gonna lose you)
I'm gonna hold you like I'm saying goodbye
Wherever we're standin', I won't take you for granted
'Cause we'll never know when, when we'll run out of time
So I'm gonna love you (I'm gonna love you, baby) like I'm gonna lose you (Like I'm gonna lose you)
I'm gonna love you (Oh) like I'm gonna lose you

snippet.title: Arthur Nery - Di Nakakasawa (Official Lyric Video)
snippet.description:
#arthurnery #dinakakasawa #thesecondalbum 

OPM’s ace male solo act Arthur Nery returns with a treat for his fans as he shares a brand new album in ‘II: The second.’ Arthur aims to shake up his usual flavors in this album as he mainly works on the songwriting and producing of the 10 tracks, along with his frequent and long-time collaborator Axel Fernandez. Each track offers a refreshing take on expressing the concept of love as he features with diverse artists like Kiyo, Jolianne, and Jon that certainly spiced it up more. Definitely, Arthur’s second album is something you should watch out for as it gives you a music experience with complex harmony and syncopated rhythms — coupled with Arthur Nery’s mesmerizing vocals.

Composed by Arthur Madrigalejos Nery Jr., Yukihiro Rubio
Published by Viva Music Publishing, Inc.
Produced by Geon Su Ganade Chung, Arthur Madrigalejos Nery Jr., Axel Fernandez
Arranged by Arthur Madrigalejos Nery Jr.
Recorded by Axel Fernandez
Mixed by Axel Fernandez
Mastered by Axel Fernandez at Runt Collective Studio

Guitar by John Apura 
Saxophone by Reymark Piquero
Drums by Bea Lao
Bass guitar by Mike Bayas
Piano by Ian Fajarito

LYRICS:
Sa dinami-dami ng nagdaan
At pumaligid sa atin
Sa atin sa ’yo pa, sa ’yo pa nakatitig
Nung ako’y handa nang magmahal

Sino ba naman 
Ang ‘di mahuhumaling
Sa ganda mo at gaan sa loob
Naapuhap na ang para sa akin
Bawal sa ’tin ang ‘di magkasama

‘Di nakakasawa
‘Di nakakasawa
Nanginig na nga sa bawat hawak
Palitan na lang ng bagong kama

Pinipigilan bawat sigaw 
Malamang sa dilim ay ako lang 
Ang gustong matanaw
At wala pa ring tama
Sa pag-iisip
Umaamin na ako sa ‘yo

‘Di nakakasawa
‘Di nakakasawa
Nanginig na nga sa bawat hawak
Palitan na lang ng bagong kama

Patalastas ang halik sa pelikula nating tagpuan
‘Di maaring malaman kung kelan ang katapusan baka kulang 
Akalain mo na gabi na kahit ‘di pa tapos sa paa 
Hmm nakakapagpabagabag
‘Pag ‘di ka na nakakasama

Hingang malalim 
Bago ko simulan
‘Di ka paawat 
Lahat hinahawakan
Isang hangarin nais niyang idaan
Labi sa labi bawat pag-aawayan

Sa ‘tin ang gabi na ‘to
Papasukin sa puso mo
Sa mundo natin na binuo
Nating dalawa, tayong dalawa

Pangako sa isat-isa
Totoong kislap ng mga mata
Salitang nagtutugma 
Puso kumanta
Ibon sumaya
Lahat tinaya
Sa ‘yo may iba
‘Di nagkaila

snippet.title: Songs for the Love We Never Forgot 💕 In the Quiet of Love, These Songs Speak Loudest
snippet.description:
Dive deep into the timeless melodies of love with "Songs for the Love We Never Forgot 💕 In the Quiet of Love, These Songs Speak Loudest."
This playlist is a heartfelt journey through memories that linger, emotions whispered in silence, and melodies that echo the unspoken feelings of the heart.
Whether you're reminiscing about a past love, cherishing quiet moments with someone special, or simply craving songs that touch the soul, these tracks will speak louder than words ever could.
💚 Let the music heal, remember, and remind you that true love never fades, even in silence.
Love is a delicate dance between holding on and letting go. It teaches us patience, forgiveness, and the courage to be vulnerable. Sometimes, love means embracing imperfections, sometimes it means learning from the pain, and sometimes it means finding beauty in the quiet moments shared between two hearts.
No matter where you are in your journey, whether your heart is full of joy or healing from loss, remember that every experience shapes the love you give and receive. True love is not always loud or obvious; often, it is found in the gentle whispers, the silent support, and the memories that never fade.
🌷🌷🌷 May these songs be a sanctuary for your heart, a reminder that you are never alone in your feelings, and that love, in all its forms, is a powerful force that connects us all. May you find comfort, hope, and strength in these melodies, and may your heart always be open to giving and receiving love freely and fearlessly.
Thank you for listening. If these songs touch your heart, please like, share, and subscribe for more soulful playlists that celebrate the beauty and complexity of love.

snippet.title: VALORANT Champions Paris — Playoffs Stage — Day 16
snippet.description:
Welcome to the climax of the 2025 VALORANT Champions Tour! The biggest stage in VALORANT is ready, the lights of Paris are shining, and the countdown has begun. Following a season of historic rivalries, epic comebacks, and unforgettable moments, the world’s top teams now gather at Champions Paris.

From September 12 to October 5, the journey continues through Group Stage and Playoffs before the epic conclusion at the Grand Final with the crowning of the next World Champion. The Group Stage will feature 16 teams spread across four groups, with each group hosting one team from VALORANT's four International Leagues. In this stage, teams will battle through a double elimination format, advancing two teams out of each group. The 8 teams who make it out will be randomly seeded into a double elimination bracket, with teams from the same group placed on opposite sides of the bracket. Teams will compete through Best-of-3 matches until the final 2 matches which will be a Best-of-5. The last team standing will claim the title of VALORANT World Champion!

We’re proud to work with our fantastic partners throughout 2025: AWS, Coinbase, EWC, HyperX, Mastercard, OMEN, Red Bull, Secretlab, and Verizon.

Make sure to follow the official VALORANT Esports social channels for additional information:
Twitter/X: @valorantesports
Facebook: /valorantesports
Instagram: @valorantesports

Twitch: https://www.twitch.tv/valorant

snippet.title: Sandali - Cup of Joe (Official Music Video)
snippet.description:
#SandaliCOJ #COJStardustTheConcert #7thJOEnniversary

To mark our 7th anniversary, we present Sandali — a song that holds a lot of meaning for us. It’s a quiet promise to one another, and to all of you who’ve stayed, listened, and grown with us through the years.

This music video is a reflection of who we are — not just as a band, but as people who’ve been through so much together. No characters, no complex narratives — just us. 

For the first time, Gab, CJ, and Xen share their voices, Gian steps into his directorial debut, and Rapha helped shape the concept from the very beginning.

Sandali also serves as the official soundtrack of our upcoming Stardust Concert Series, kicking off next week at The Big Dome! We hope this gives you a glimpse of the feeling, energy, and heart we’re bringing to the show.

Explore the dark side of the cosmos with the new Cosmic Scenery, or completely transform your Heroes into shockingly spooky villains with Cosmic Hero Skins. A Cosmic Curse has come!

#clashoween
Follow us on our Socials!
Twitter ► https://twitter.com/ClashofClans/
Instagram ► https://www.instagram.com/clashofclans 
Facebook ► https://www.facebook.com/ClashofClans 
TikTok ► https://www.tiktok.com/@clashofclans

Attack. Defend. Strategize. Download for free for mobile devices. supr.cl/PlayClashOfClans

From rage-­filled Barbarians with glorious mustaches to pyromaniac wizards, raise your own army and lead your clan to victory! Build your village to fend off raiders, battle against millions of players worldwide, and forge a powerful clan with others to destroy enemy clans.
PLEASE NOTE! Clash of Clans is free to download and play, however some game items can also be purchased for real money 

Also, under our Terms of Service and Privacy Policy, you must be at least 13 years of age to play or download Clash of Clans.
A network connection is also required.

FEATURES
- Build your village into an unbeatable fortress 
- Raise your own army of Barbarians, Archers, Hog Riders, Wizards, Dragons and other mighty fighters
- Battle with players worldwide and take their Trophies
- Join together with other players to form the ultimate Clan
- Fight against rival Clans in epic Clan Wars 
- Build 18 unique units with multiple levels of upgrades
- Discover your favorite attacking army from countless combinations of troops, spells, Heroes and Clan reinforcements 
- Defend your village with a multitude of Cannons, Towers, Mortars, Bombs, Traps and Walls
- Fight against the Goblin King in a campaign through the realm

Chief, are you having problems? Visit https://help.supercellsupport.com/clash-of-clans/en/
